parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or shift into neutral unexpectedly, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power

the vehicle has difficulty accelerating
the vehicle has a loud whining or grinding noise
the check engine light or transmission warning light illuminates.
